Revision history for File-Slurp-Shortcuts

0.05     2014-02-26 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Add 'use experimental smartmatch' for perl
           5.18+.


0.04     2013-09-09 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Rebuild with MakeMaker instead of
           Module::Build because the latter is deprecated from core in 5.19.


0.03    2011-02-08 (SHARYANTO)

        - Rename module from File::Slurp::Chomp -> File::Slurp::Shortcuts.


0.02    2011-02-04 (SHARYANTO)

        - Add read_file_c/slurp_c and read_file_q/slurp_q.


0.01    2011-02-04 (SHARYANTO)

        - First release.
